description: Welcome to the PH2 at 45 West Broadway.  This is the first time this incredible condo has ever been offered for sale.  It is truly one of a kind loaded in history and architecturally beautiful.  Saint Peter and Paul church was built in the 1840s and many details remain.  One of the most stunning features is an original stain glass close to 20 high in length.  It is of Saint Cecilla who was the saint of music and arts.  It will take your breath away. The condo has 2 bedroom suites with a sitting area and stairs to lead to a lofted bed, ceiling height sore to 20 feet.  You must see to appreciate.
